					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Disch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">6:14:30  (NEStopia uses this setting I'd assume?)</div>
<br />That is correct.  This is the "official" time used in the actual tournament.
<br />
<br />I'm not sure why you'd get different times with each test.  I found out the special mode by examing the ROM in a hex editor.  As soon as the ROM detects the combination, it starts the timer and immediately starts counting frames (i.e. both the on-screen timer and the IRQ timer start within 1 frame of each other).  I'll look through it again in case I overlooked something.</div>

					
