					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">rbudrick wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">So what's the special mode?</div><br />Read my post above.  While at the title screen, on controller #2, hold A and press SELECT.<br /><div class="quotetitle">rbudrick wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">And why is the REAL time (about 6:21 as opposed to 6:15 for competition time) slightly longer than what the cart is set to per the label and the results in this thread?<br /><br />-Rob</div>
<br />The IRQ timer doesn't start until right before SMB starts, or about 390 frames (6.5 seconds) after you press Start on controller #2.
<br />
<br />I finished going through the startup code on NWC.  At the title screen, the code responds to four things:
<br />
<br />1) A+SELECT on controller #2 (IRQ test mode)
<br />2) B+SELECT on controller #2 (starts the contest, but skips SMB)
<br />3) START on controller #2 (starts contest)
<br />4) Trigger pulled on Light Gun (starts contest - haven't tested this one)</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />"Last version was better," says Floyd. "More bugs. Bugs make game fun."</div>
