						<div class="postbody">Small correction is due.  The NWC is not listening for Light Gun input.  It appears instead to have been written with a custom peripheral in mind.  The zapper sends the trigger status on $4017.D4, whereas the NWC code monitors $4017.D3 instead.</div>

					
